  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-5 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are either fully assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel, or scoped-out with thorough documented rationale. Two factors — Equivalency of input parameters and Use error — are scoped-out with paragraph-level justification. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 5 flow-speed operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
